title: Devouring Realm
description: Devouring Realm In his previous life, Qiu Lin lost his most cherished partner due to his own mistakes. In order to defend the honor of the trade union, he tried his best to die with the enemy. Now, the reborn Qiu Lin has returned to the starting point of everything. In order to make up for the regrets of the previous life, he will fight to… Devour The World Devouring Zone Return Of Soul Master 吞噬领域
